item.title: CVE-2020-2592|2024-08-04T07:09:54.833Z -- oracle%20corporation -- autovue%203d%20professional%20advanced
item.description: Vulnerability in the Oracle AutoVue product of Oracle Supply Chain (component: Security). The supported version that is affected is 21.0.2. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows unauthenticated attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle AutoVue. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized read access to a subset of Oracle AutoVue accessible data. CVSS 3.0 Base Score 5.3 (Confidentiality impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.0/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N).

item.title: CVE-2020-14551|2024-08-04T12:46:34.898Z -- oracle%20corporation -- autovue%203d%20professional%20advanced
item.description: Vulnerability in the Oracle AutoVue product of Oracle Supply Chain (component: Security). The supported version that is affected is 21.0. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows low privileged attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle AutoVue. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized update, insert or delete access to some of Oracle AutoVue accessible data. CVSS 3.1 Base Score 4.3 (Integrity impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:L/A:N).

item.title: CVE-2019-2575|2024-08-04T18:56:44.043Z -- oracle%20corporation -- autovue%203d%20professional%20advanced
item.description: Vulnerability in the Oracle AutoVue 3D Professional Advanced component of Oracle Supply Chain Products Suite (subcomponent: Format Handling - 2D). Supported versions that are affected are 21.0.0 and 21.0.1. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows unauthenticated attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle AutoVue 3D Professional Advanced. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized read access to a subset of Oracle AutoVue 3D Professional Advanced accessible data. CVSS 3.0 Base Score 5.3 (Confidentiality impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.0/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N).
